title: Hitler The Junkie
description:
Hitler The Junkie

Morphine. Crystal meth. Sedatives. Testosterone. Leeches. A German soldier's feces. A bizarre combination of substances, but just a few of the more than 70 different drugs, vitamins and concoctions Adolf Hitler was consuming during the last nine years of his reign. This hard-hitting and in-depth film sets out to examine the medications Hitler was on, how often and how much he took, and to explore if drugs played a role in his behaviour and actions
